# Environment variables — never commit live values.
# `.env*` is a deliberate catch-all (matches .env, .env.local, .env.bak,
# .env.bak.<ts>, .envrc, .environment, etc.). Only the two template files
# committed for new contributors are whitelisted.
.env*
!.env.example
!.env.test

